# Energy Dashboard Project Context

## Project Overview

Interactive energy capacity dashboard deployed on Cloudflare Workers at https://energy.gsaboia.workers.dev

## Current Architecture

- **Runtime**: Cloudflare Workers
- **Frontend**: Vanilla HTML/CSS/JavaScript
- **Charts**: Chart.js library
- **Data**: Embedded JSON with country-specific data
- **Deployment**: Cloudflare Pages with Git integration

## Key Files

- [src/index.ts](mdc:src/index.ts) - Worker entry point
- [public/index.html](mdc:public/index.html) - Dashboard UI
- [public/script.js](mdc:public/script.js) - Chart functionality
- [public/style.css](mdc:public/style.css) - Styling
- [README.md](mdc:README.md) - Project documentation

## Current Features

- Monthly time series data (2023-2025)
- Country-specific data (Global, US, China)
- 5 chart types: bar, percentage, time series, delta analysis
- Interactive period/country selection with optimized performance
- Source attribution system
- GPU-accelerated animations and transitions

## Development Preferences

- Spartan tone in responses
- Git integration with 'master' branch (not 'main')
- Concise documentation in docs/ directory
- Cloudflare Pages deployment preference

